before.enText: not used in the progressive tenses

data.enText: to look like or be similar to another person or thing

data.chText: 许多酒店看上去都差不多。
data.enText: So many hotels resemble each other.
The plant resembles grass in appearance.

simple_means.memory_skill: re 一再 + sembl 相类似，一样 + e → 再怎么都一样 → 类似

tr: be similar or bear a likeness to
example: She resembles her mother very much
This paper resembles my own work

value.def: If one thing or person resembles another, they are similar to each other.

example.ex: Some of the commercially produced venison resembles beef in flavour...
example.tran: 有些商业化养殖的鹿肉味道和牛肉很相似。
